dge now what is manifested outwardly of your deeds.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17374,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/28\/do-not-wish-for-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":2078,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Mawt: Do not wish for death, you might repent","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLet none of you wish for death. If he is a good-doer, he might increase his good deeds. If he is an evil-doer, he might make amends.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7235 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3258,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/21\/good-deeds-multiplied\/","url_meta":{"origin":2078,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Favor: Allah multiplies good deeds for believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you practices Islam well, every good deed he does is written as ten good deeds up to seven hundred times as much, and every bad deed he does is written as one bad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u062